# No Co-authored-by Cursor on commits

When creating commits in this repo:

- Do **not** include `Co-authored-by: Cursor` / `Co-authored-by: *cursor*` / AI attribution trailers
- Do **not** use Cursor flags or templates that inject a co-author automatically
- Message = clean Conventional Commits (type/scope/subject + body when needed)

Forbidden:

```text
feat: add header contact icons

Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>
```

OK:

```text
feat: add header contact icons
```
